This has no filter.  No kira kira .  Nothing .  Just point and shot.  Thats how insane this backpack is.  All @swarovski .  Marc Jacobs x KimJones Fendi .  Who knows if theyll make more of these.  But I couldnt not show this .

This backpack is a work of art.  I cant get over the insanity.  I did not use any filters,  any kira kira,  no lights ,  No tricks this is just how this backpack looks .  It is completely covered in Swarovski crystals.  Its one of one (for now.) from the Marc Jacobs X Kim Jones Fendi  New York collection. (Theres a Fendi baguette as well like this thats insane. )  #FendiRoma High Snobiety better peep this.
Yo!!!!!! @winnieharlow why didnt u put me on game?! Lol . This shit is 💣💣💣 @cayskin  My lips are so soft.

Beautiful night with the beautiful bestie.  First time at the legendary @apollotheater  seeing everyone come together and sing in unison was such an amazing reminder  of the power of music. A 2am trip for ice cream in the snow with RR 😝🍦. Then slumber party at the telly . Could not have asked for a more perfect night.  Feeling very grateful.

Thank you so much @geronimojr and Karen for inviting us to take the legendary Bobby Ore’s driving class.  Since everyone is gonna ask,  Heres their page @bobby_ore_motorsports .  Its in Sebring , FL,  we took the 2 day stunt driving class.  They teach stunt driving, drifting, tactical defense, military, secret service.  So whether youre trying to evade an attack,  or pap’z cameras. Or just need an advatage to get into a parking spot quickly in NYC 😜😎 they can teach you anything.  Forget everything you think you know about driving . This class was so humbling as well as such a challenge mentally,  physically, everything.  Im so grateful for it and for the amazing instructors they have. (@amytcheek  and #Greg) They are such beasts behind the wheel and have so much grace and patience when they teach.  Im def going back for the 3 day drifting…  Who in?
